N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4810.4 - Validity of identification number

State Regulations

The identification number shall be valid until suspended, revoked or surrendered. The commission may suspend the identification number of
any registered organization that has not been licensed to conduct bingo during
four consecutive months and should such suspension be imposed, the organization
concerned shall request reinstatement prior to making application for a bingo
license. Notes
